{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A day at school has never been this thrilling! Izumi Sensei, your ruthless teacher with a dark side, has been terrorizing the students for far too long. It\u2019s time to teach her a lesson she\u2019ll never forget\u2014by pranking her at every turn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you outsmart Izumi Sensei, or will her sharp instincts catch you in the act? Your mission: cause as much chaos as possible, and maybe even make her regret all those cruel punishments. After all, revenge is sweet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a hilarious 3D anime world full of tricky pranks and surprises!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Outsmart and prank the terrifying Izumi Sensei, but beware\u2014she's always watching!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore different parts of the school and unlock hidden areas for the perfect prank.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your character with fun anime-style accessories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Laugh, plot, and prank your way through this wild adventure as you teach Izumi Sensei that payback can be fun!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730465673","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307110/page.bg.jpg?t=1730465673","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307110/1bfbdfebd66c254fdb4764d84f1a77815f88a9bc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730465673","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307110/1bfbdfebd66c254fdb4764d84f1a77815f88a9bc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730465673","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A day at school has never been th